    "name": "Scarecrow",
    "steam_appid": 2280360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/2c4292c561c53ba8bdbc0c7ce349f54c.avif?t=1771422580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras_big/2c4292c561c53ba8bdbc0c7ce349f54c.avif?t=1771422580 width=1560 height=312 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/8e8326c7e86352d9e688de02027ec5bf.avif?t=1771422580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras_big/8e8326c7e86352d9e688de02027ec5bf.webp?t=1771422580 width=1560 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are hitman fox with a shadowy backstory.</strong> Your days drag on one after another: identical and hopeless. The turbulent '90s are raging – a time of lawlessness and brutality. In the small, impoverished town of Severodvishchensk, populated by humans and anthropomorphic animals, criminal gangs are clawing for power, dragging all the other down into the abyss. And all of a sudden you find yourself right at the center of it all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your job is to rub the nuisances out of your client's list, who has spun his web of shady connections across the entire city. But sooner or later, every web tears. Where will this criminal path lead you? Will you manage to unravel the mysteries of your own past?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/7132aac1cbbbac44bc80d85ebf42e00a.avif?t=1771422580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras_big/7132aac1cbbbac44bc80d85ebf42e00a.webp?t=1771422580 width=1560 height=176 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The gameplay cycle is divided into 2 phases: DAY and NIGHT.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the day, explore a vast, living city filled with interesting characters: from the cute, kind-hearted cat Sasha to the stinking bum Timokha. Every day in Severodvishchensk, something interesting happens, and the city won't let you get bored. Have fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/ee4e273d67e6e0f6516f3c05c8c43679.poster.avif?t=1771422580\" width=1170 height=526 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/ee4e273d67e6e0f6516f3c05c8c43679.webm?t=1771422580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/ee4e273d67e6e0f6516f3c05c8c43679.mp4?t=1771422580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>At night, everything changes.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ruthlessly crush your enemies, combining fury with tactics. You’ll have over 20 diverse weapons, multiplied by Robert's agility. Use them wisely! You will face dangerous foes, clearing out mansions, gangster bathhouses, city offices, drug labs, getting ever more entangled in this criminal web.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for an adrenaline rush – you'll need to quickly adapt to the constantly changing situation while in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/8bf4004496fe87dcdfbfcdc2858828db.poster.avif?t=1771422580\" width=1170 height=526 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/8bf4004496fe87dcdfbfcdc2858828db.webm?t=1771422580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/8bf4004496fe87dcdfbfcdc2858828db.mp4?t=1771422580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/a4ca1be99cde8fa6c564b3c78ae78047.avif?t=1771422580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras_big/a4ca1be99cde8fa6c564b3c78ae78047.webp?t=1771422580 width=1560 height=176 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A rich storyline full of secrets, drama, and hope for the best</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pixel art with every pixel lovingly honed</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A vast atmospheric city of the turbulent '90s, waiting just for you</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic gangster shootouts with a wide choice of weapons and tactics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dialogue choices that affect the plot and the story's ending</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An amazing soundtrack by Xis350, isekaifromsaratov, Myasorubin, and other cool musicians!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find warmth in this cold place, or freeze for good</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/d35ac0a415dbb764434f3729e3e8ac12.poster.avif?t=1771422580\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/d35ac0a415dbb764434f3729e3e8ac12.webm?t=1771422580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/d35ac0a415dbb764434f3729e3e8ac12.mp4?t=1771422580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/af85890b537bf507d9600e6063c17b8e.avif?t=1771422580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras_big/af85890b537bf507d9600e6063c17b8e.webp?t=1771422580 width=1560 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scarecrow is being developed by ChillouT Studio</strong>, an indie team of 4 people. You can learn more about everyone involved in the development on the game's official website.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scarecrow consists of three chapters. All chapters are included in the game's price and will be added automatically as they are completed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Add the game to your wishlist and help us promote the project. Release in 2026!</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras/2c4292c561c53ba8bdbc0c7ce349f54c.avif?t=1771422580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280360/extras_big/2c4292c561c53ba8bdbc0c7ce349f54c.avif?t=1771422580 width=1560 height=312 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
